   "cell_type": "code",

     "outputs_hidden": false

   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "data = sm.datasets.sunspots.load()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Right now an annual date series must be datetimes at the end of the year."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2024-10-24T10:40:47.000292Z",

    "jupyter": {
     "outputs_hidden": false
    }
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from datetime import datetime\n",
    "\n",
    "dates = pd.date_range(\"1700-1-1\", periods=len(data.endog), freq=\"YE-DEC\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [

    "endog = data.endog\n",
    "endog"

   "source": [

  {
   "cell_type": "code",

   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2024-10-24T10:40:47.025161Z",

     "outputs_hidden": false

   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "selection_res = ar_select_order(endog, 9, old_names=False, seasonal=True, period=11)\n",
    "pandas_ar_res = selection_res.model.fit()"
